latestIgtvVideos.title: I AM ENOUGH
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
LOVE WITH PRIDE🌈

Thought:-

These two were on their road to journey just like thousands of other similar faces.
A perplexed state of mind haunted their inner conscience.
Is this even normal? Is this even right?
Questions and doubts bombarded their preconceived notions of normality. 

But, reality struck hard when they realised the importance of being true and the real you! 
That surpassed the negativity and resulted in BELIEVING.

Loving the person who you want is easy. You're the only judge and the jury! 

All you need to do is accept yourself and the world can wait untill you're on your own, better  than the rest. 

LOVE IS LOVE!🌈
